## Code Protection & Anti-Patterns
- ALWAYS read before modifying, respect existing patterns
- Working code: ASK before changing
- Avoid: Scope explosion, phantom fix (verify: IDENTIFY→RUN→READ→VERIFY→CLAIM), cargo cult config, courtesy review (min. 5 findings), silent failure, stub blindness, context amnesia, over-engineering, littering

## Skills & Plugins
- Before complex actions: Check for matching skill in ~/.claude/skills/
- Prefer plugins when available
